# Copy to .npmrc and update the Python path for your system
# 
# For native module compilation (better-sqlite3), npm needs Python 3.8+
#
# If using uv (recommended):
#   1. Install uv: curl -LsSf https://astral.sh/uv/install.sh | sh
#   2. Install Python: uv python install 3.12
#   3. Find path: uv python find 3.12
#   4. Set below
#
# Example:
# python=/Users/yourname/.local/share/uv/python/cpython-3.12-macos-aarch64-none/bin/python3.12
